Use Case Diagram (Actors & Interactions)

Actors:

1) Mentor

2) Mentee

3) Admin (future)

Use Cases:

1) Mentor:

  ->Login / Signup

  ->Create Resource

  ->Manage Resources (Edit/Delete)

  ->View Mentee Progress

2) Mentee:

  ->Login / Signup

  ->View Learning Path

  ->View Resource (Video, Help Doc, FAQ, Quiz, Ticket)

  ->Submit Quiz / Update Progress

3) Admin (Future):

  ->Track Analytics

  ->Generate AI Suggestions

Diagram:

+------------------+
|      User        |
+------------------+
| - userId         |
| - name           |
| - email          |
| - role (Mentor/Mentee) |
+------------------+
| + login()        |
| + signup()       |
+------------------+

          ▲
          │
 ┌────────┴────────┐
 |                 |
 |                 |
 v                 v
+------------------+        +------------------+
|     Mentor       |        |     Mentee       |
+------------------+        +------------------+
| +createResource()|        | +viewResources() |
| +manageResources()|       | +submitQuiz()    |
| +viewProgress()  |        | +trackProgress() |
+------------------+        +------------------+

+------------------+
|    Resource      |
+------------------+
| - resourceId     |
| - title          |
| - description    |
| - category       |
+------------------+
| +addSubmodule()  |
| +editResource()  |
| +deleteResource()|
+------------------+
          │
          ├───────────────────────────────────────────┐
          │                                           │
   ┌─────────────┐ ┌───────────────┐ ┌───────────────┐ ┌───────────────┐ ┌───────────────┐
   │   Video     │ │   HelpDoc     │ │     FAQ       │ │     Quiz      │ │    Ticket     │
   +-------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+
   | id          | | id            | | id            | | id            | | id            |
   | title       | | title         | | question      | | question      | | title         |
   | url         | | content       | | answer        | | options[]     | | issueDesc     |
   |              |                 |                 | | correctAnswer | | resolution    |
   +-------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+

+--------------------------+
|     ProgressTracker      |
+--------------------------+
| - menteeId               |
| - resourceId             |
| - status (NotStarted/InProgress/Completed) |
| - quizScore              |
+--------------------------+
| +updateProgress()        |
| +getProgress()           |
+--------------------------+
